#For this project, I used SQL to query the Superstore database to get information about items sold at the store and their prices. 

1 --Write a SQL query that orders the items by price.
2
3 SELECT * FROM superstore
4 ORDER BY price;
5​
6 --Show an SQL query to show a sum about the item prices.
7​
8 SELECT SUM(stock_quantity) FROM superstore;
9​
10 --Write a SQL query that will show a statistic about the price for items in the category of "Kitchen Supplies".
11
12 SELECT price FROM superstore
13 WHERE category = 'Kitchen Supplies';
14
15 --Write a query to show how many air purifiers are in stock.
16​
17 SELECT (stock_quantity)
18 FROM superstore
19 WHERE item_name = 'Air Purifier';

